sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Customer
    participant F as React Frontend
    participant A as Express API
    participant OCR as Tesseract OCR
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant FDA as OpenFDA API
    participant P as Pharmacist
    
    C->>F: Upload prescription image
    F->>A: POST /api/prescriptions/upload
    A->>DB: Save image URL & create record
    DB-->>A: Prescription ID
    
    A->>OCR: Process image (async)
    Note over OCR: OCR accuracy: 70-85%
    OCR-->>A: Extracted text
    A->>DB: Update extracted_text
    A-->>F: Prescription created (status: Processing)
    F-->>C: Upload successful
    
    P->>F: Review prescription
    F->>A: GET /api/prescriptions/:id
    A->>DB: Fetch prescription
    DB-->>A: Prescription data
    A-->>F: Prescription details
    
    P->>F: Edit & verify prescription
    F->>A: PUT /api/prescriptions/:id/verify
    A->>FDA: Check drug interactions
    FDA-->>A: Interaction warnings (if any)
    
    alt No interactions
        A->>DB: Update status to 'Verified'
        A-->>F: Verification successful
        F-->>P: Ready to dispense
    else Interactions found
        A-->>F: Warning: Drug interactions
        F-->>P: Show warnings
        P->>F: Confirm override OR reject
    end
    
    P->>F: Process sale (POS)
    F->>A: POST /api/sales
    A->>DB: Create sale & update inventory
    A->>DB: Update prescription status to 'Dispensed'
    A-->>F: Sale completed
    F-->>P: Invoice generated
    F-->>C: Medicine dispensed
